President Donald J. Trump has made several appointments for the Executive Office of the President. Dan J. Scavino will be the Assistant to the President and Deputy Chief of Staff for Communications. John C. Fleming, M.D., will be the Assistant to the President for Planning and Implementation. Kayleigh McEnany will serve as the Assistant to the President and Press Secretary. Alyssa Farah will be the Assistant to the President and Director of Strategic Communications. Nicholas F. Luna will serve as the Assistant to the President and Director of Oval Office Operations.